<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= pageTitle %> | MyTaxCalcs</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Use the free tax refund calculator to estimate your federal refund or amount owed based on income, deductions, credits, withholding, and estimated payments.">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/>
            <rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span>MyTaxCalcs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="/calculators">All Calculators</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="calc-hero">
    <div class="calc-hero-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Federal Refund Estimator</div>
      <h1>Tax Refund Calculator</h1>
      <p>Estimate whether you may receive a federal tax refund or owe additional federal tax.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="calc-main">
    <div class="calc-layout">
      <section class="calc-form-card">
        <div class="calc-form-header">
          <div class="calc-form-icon" style="background:#f0fdf4; color:#16a34a;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Your Tax Information</h2>
        </div>
        <form method="POST" action="/tax-refund-calculator" class="calc-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Gross Annual Income</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="grossIncome" value="<%= form.grossIncome || '' %>" placeholder="85,000" required></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Filing Status</label>
            <select name="filingStatus">
              <option value="single" <%= form.filingStatus === "single" ? "selected" : "" %>>Single</option>
              <option value="marriedJoint" <%= form.filingStatus === "marriedJoint" ? "selected" : "" %>>Married Filing Jointly</option>
              <option value="marriedSeparate" <%= form.filingStatus === "marriedSeparate" ? "selected" : "" %>>Married Filing Separately</option>
              <option value="headHousehold" <%= form.filingStatus === "headHousehold" ? "selected" : "" %>>Head of Household</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Deduction Type</label>
            <select name="deductionType">
              <option value="standard" <%= !form.deductionType || form.deductionType === "standard" ? "selected" : "" %>>Standard Deduction</option>
              <option value="itemized" <%= form.deductionType === "itemized" ? "selected" : "" %>>Itemized Deduction</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Itemized Deduction Amount</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="itemizedDeduction" value="<%= form.itemizedDeduction || '' %>" placeholder="0"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Federal Tax Withheld</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="federalWithheld" value="<%= form.federalWithheld || '' %>" placeholder="12,000"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Estimated Tax Payments</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="estimatedPayments" value="<%= form.estimatedPayments || '' %>" placeholder="0"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Other Tax Payments</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="otherPayments" value="<%= form.otherPayments || '' %>" placeholder="0"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Non-Refundable Tax Credits</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="nonRefundableCredits" value="<%= form.nonRefundableCredits || '' %>" placeholder="0"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Refundable Tax Credits</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="refundableCredits" value="<%= form.refundableCredits || '' %>" placeholder="0"></div>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="calc-submit-btn">Calculate Refund Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="calc-results-card">
        <div class="calc-form-header">
          <div class="calc-form-icon" style="background:#f0fdf4; color:#16a34a;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Estimated Results</h2>
        </div>
        <% if (!result) { %>
          <div class="results-empty">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
            <p>Enter your income, withholding, payments, and credits to estimate your refund or amount owed.</p>
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="results-grid">
            <div class="result-row"><span>Tax Year</span><strong><%= result.taxYear %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Gross Income</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.grossIncome).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Deduction</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.deduction).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Taxable Income</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.taxableIncome).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Federal Tax Before Credits</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.federalTaxBeforeCredits).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Non-Refundable Credits</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.nonRefundableCredits).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Tax After Credits</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.federalTaxAfterNonRefundableCredits).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Federal Tax Withheld</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.federalWithheld).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Estimated Payments</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.estimatedPayments).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Refundable Credits</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.refundableCredits).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Total Payments & Credits</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.totalPayments).toLocaleString() %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row result-highlight <%= result.refundOrOwed >= 0 ? 'refund' : 'owed' %>">
              <% if (result.refundOrOwed >= 0) { %>
                <span>Estimated Refund</span><strong>$<%= Math.round(result.refundOrOwed).toLocaleString() %></strong>
              <% } else { %>
                <span>Estimated Amount Owed</span><strong>$<%= Math.abs(Math.round(result.refundOrOwed)).toLocaleString() %></strong>
              <% } %>
            </div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Effective Tax Rate</span><strong><%= (result.effectiveTaxRate * 100).toFixed(1) %>%</strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Marginal Tax Rate</span><strong><%= (result.marginalRate * 100).toFixed(1) %>%</strong></div>
          </div>
        <% } %>
        <div class="results-disclaimer">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          Estimate only. Not tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice.
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="calc-content-wrapper">
      <section class="content seo-content">
        <p class="eyebrow dark">Tax Refund Guide</p>
        <h2>How this tax refund calculator works</h2>
        <p>This tax refund calculator estimates whether you may receive a federal refund or owe additional tax by comparing your estimated federal tax liability with your withholding, estimated payments, other payments, and refundable credits.</p>
        <div class="seo-grid">
          <div class="seo-mini-card"><h3>Refund estimate</h3><p>A refund may occur when total tax payments and refundable credits are greater than your estimated federal tax after non-refundable credits.</p></div>
          <div class="seo-mini-card"><h3>Amount owed estimate</h3><p>You may owe additional tax if your estimated federal tax is greater than your withholding, estimated payments, other payments, and refundable credits.</p></div>
          <div class="seo-mini-card"><h3>Credits and payments</h3><p>Non-refundable credits can reduce your tax to zero. Refundable credits and payments can increase your refund estimate.</p></div>
        </div>
        <h2>Tax refund FAQ</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>What is a tax refund?</h3><p>A tax refund is money returned to you when your tax payments and refundable credits are greater than your final tax liability.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>Why might I owe taxes instead of getting a refund?</h3><p>You may owe taxes if not enough was withheld from your paycheck, if you had self-employment income, investment income, fewer credits, or other taxable income without enough payments.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>What is the difference between non-refundable and refundable credits?</h3><p>A non-refundable credit can reduce your tax liability, but generally does not create a refund by itself. A refundable credit may increase your refund even if your tax is already zero.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>Does this calculator include state refunds?</h3><p>No. This calculator focuses on federal refund estimates. State tax refunds depend on each state's tax rules, withholding, credits, and filing requirements.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>Can I use this to file my taxes?</h3><p>No. This calculator is for educational estimates only. For filing, use official tax forms, tax software, or a qualified tax professional.</p></div>
        </div>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </section>
      <section class="content related-calculators">
        <p class="eyebrow dark">Related Calculators</p>
        <h2>More tax calculators</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/income-tax-calculator">Income Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/self-employment-tax-calculator">Self-Employment Tax</a>
          <a href="/capital-gains-tax-calculator">Capital Gains Tax</a>
          <a href="/sales-tax-calculator">Sales Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/payroll-tax-calculator">Payroll Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/calculators">All Calculators</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="footer-logo"><span class="logo-mark"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/><rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/></svg></span>MyTaxCalcs</a>
          <p>Free tax calculators for income tax, refunds, self-employment tax, capital gains tax, sales tax, payroll tax, and state income tax estimates.</p>
        </div>
